0.13    2017-01-13 (PERLANCAR)

        - No functional changes.

        - [build] Rebuild with fixed Perinci::CmdLine::POD 0.005 (fix env and
          config filenames in POD).


0.12    2017-01-13 (PERLANCAR)

        - No functional changes.

        - [dist] Force upgrade of Perinci::CmdLine::Lite to 1.71 (to get
          implicit path encoding).


0.11    2017-01-13 (PERLANCAR)

	- Remove manual ~ prefix resolving in directory arguments because
	  they are now handled by Config::IOD::Reader 0.31+.


0.10    2017-01-13 (PERLANCAR)

	- Add subcommand: duplicate (to list long directories that have
	  more than one shorts).


0.09    2015-09-12 (PERLANCAR)

	- Allow cds completion to do fuzzy matching.


0.08    2015-06-13 (PERLANCAR)

        - No functional changes.

        - [build] Rebuild, end testing of using Perinci::CmdLine::Any::Lumped.
          Back to using regular Perinci::CmdLine::Any distribution.


